<br />\n如果無美國，我相信日本好容易由極權主義轉到中國特色嘅共產主義，因為本質基本上係一樣而且果時嘅日本人比較容易洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1014a70575c5e753f6beaed9973e35092495ce8","tid":1972409,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}